330
00:22:57,910 --> 00:22:59,150
Send as many men as needed

331
00:22:59,510 --> 00:23:00,720
and find out the truth.

332
00:23:00,910 --> 00:23:01,600
Yes.

333
00:23:02,320 --> 00:23:03,200
Mr. Guo of Justice

334
