with the cutlass.

437
00:28:37,030 --> 00:28:39,510
So you mean...

438
00:28:43,360 --> 00:28:45,960
The cutlass is still in the hall.

439
00:28:47,840 --> 00:28:48,630
Find it.

440
00:28:49,150 --> 00:28:50,480
Take men to find it.

441
00:28:51,110 --> 00:28:52,150
Yes, Your Majesty.

